It works really well as a radiator in cold places. I am hoping to take it 
with me to north Sweden as a hand warmer. In all seriousness through, this 
is a great upgrade from FFRS 3 and I love the added features which make it 
more realistic and involving. Little details like if you give your guests 
an intense ride that they throw up and the person taking money and other 
ride attendants are great additions. God almighty it takes so much power 
though! Also a few glitches with some rides in certain scenarios and the 
super slow parking mechanism reduce the star rating.
